data.description: MASSIVE PRICE IMPROVEMENT! Possible VA Assumption at 2.875% APR FOR A VA ELIGIBLE BORROWER!!! Welcome Home to this beautiful water view property in Hunting Run Reservoir. Situated on 5.5 acres of rolling pastures, this 2022 Modern Farmhouse is sure to please. Relax by sitting on the front porch or entertaining your family and friends in the gourmet kitchen around the massive center island adorned with an oversized farm style sink wrapped in the quartz countertops. Prepare a meal on the gas cooktop and in the high-end GE stainless steel Cafe' Selection wall oven /microwave combo. The main level has an office /flex space, dining room, bedroom, open kitchen /dining /living space, laundry room, walk-in pantry, and a large powder room large enough to accommodate a tub /shower should one be desired by the future owner. The large foyer boasts an angled staircase leading to the wide and open upstairs hallway.  Upstairs includes 4 spacious bedrooms and 3 full and unique bathrooms. Unwind from the day in the gorgeous spa-like master bathroom features a large walk-in shower, stand alone soaking tub, and double vanity. The open unfinished walkout basement offers endless opportunity to add personalization. The property even features your very own baseball diamond with fenced backdrop. THE COPPER RANGE HOOD DOES NOT CONVEY AND WILL BE REMOVED PRIOR TO SETTLEMENT.
